INUMBER 866
NAME 776
MISC
WEIGHT 3
VOLUME 3
IFPREVERB LOOK -1
  CLEARVERB
   IFVAR ITEMADJ3 = 77
     ECHO PLAYER Crystal of sheer perfection has been formed into a dazzling harp. Golden strings, dusted with powdered diamond, flow seamlessly from top to bottom in the center of the instrument, while the essence of captured stars flow beautifully througout the crystal surface.
   ENDIF
    IFVAR ITEMADJ3 = 292
      ECHO PLAYER Formed of pure silver with delicate strands of shimmering silver for strings the beautiful instrument is engraved with slowly creeping rose vines that nearly seem to burst free from the instrument with blooming brilliance.
    ENDIF
