NUMBER 2534
NAME Hunan's void
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
Light filters slowly throughout the expanse of this shapeless chamber
illuminating everything with a muted sea-blue glow. The light bends
gently around the chamber's single accoutrement, a candle lit altar
devoted to the worship of Amilor. Walls flicker imperceptibly at the
edge of your vision, yet fade into the light when you attempt to
look directly at them. There seem to be no exits from this serene
place.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 236 ADJ1=347 ADJ2=187
EXTEND 0 with candles flickering atop it
ITEM 1 495 ADJ1=287 ADJ2=292
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 0
The gentle blue light flows over the polished marble of the altar and
the engravings of Amilor found thereupon, like the rolling waves of the
ocean. A shimmering silver inscription has been delicately engraved in
the center of the altar.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM READ 1
         "To you, Father, I send my prayers,"
    "In the gentle rush of the ocean's waves, you answer."
 "In the roar of thunder that precedes the spring rain, you answer."
"And in my heart do I know that you walk beside me, now and forever."
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFVERB LISTEN -1
  ECHO PLAYER You hear the muted sounds of waves crashing against the gentle shore, and your mind fills with serene peace.
ENDIF
;
NUMBER 2531
NAME The Sacred Grove
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
CHANNEL 115
*DESCRIPTION_START
Twilight fills this quiet grove with peaceful solitude. A light dusting
of snow glazes the surrounding trees with a sparkling silver. In the
center, illuminated only by the light of the overhead stars and the
bright moon, stands a simple shrine to the Lady. It is a circle of pillars
with no walls, only a translucent ceiling that lets in the light of the
stars, and a single arch that leads to its interior. A carved wooden bench
beckons invitingly from under the sheltering branches of a great oak.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 60 VAL2=2533
ITEM 1 229 ADJ1=216
VARIABLE monkatel
IFVERB LISTEN -1
   ECHO PLAYER The hush of the surrounding forest is broken ony by the mournful hoot of a snowy owl.
   ECHO OTHERS %N smiles gently as beatific calm washes over %h features.
ENDIF
IFVERB SMELL -1
   ECHO PLAYER The cool air nips at your nose as you inhale the clean, crisp mountain air, tasting pine and cedar on the gentle wind.
ENDIF
IFSAY My_spirit_is_rested,_My_lady.
   ECHO PLAYER Glittering starlight descends from the gentle sky, wrapping you in safety and carrying you back to the Solarium.
   ECHO OTHERS %N is wrapped in glittering starlight, fading from your view a moment thereafter.
   MOVE 2676
   AFFECT 2676
   ECHO OTHERS %N appears, glittering starlight playing around %i.
   AFFECT 2531
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GO 1
  CLEARVERB
  AFFECT 2532
  EQUAL monkatel PLRSINROOM
  AFFECT 2531
   IFVAR monkatel > 0
     ECHO PLAYER There is someone there already, you don't feel like disturbing them.
     ECHO OTHERS %N moves towards the bench and then stops.
   ENDIF
    IFVAR monkatel = 0
      DISBAND
      ECHO PLAYER You duck under some low branches and sit beneath the great oak.
      ECHO OTHERS %N ducks under some low branches and sits beneath the great oak.
      MOVE 2532
      POSITION SIT
      EQUAL ROUNDTIME 5
    ENDIF
ENDIF
;
NUMBER 2532
NAME Beneath the Oak
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
CHANNEL 115
*DESCRIPTION_START
A snowy owl sits across from you, eyes bright in the starlight. A few
snowflakes drift downward through the branches of the great oak,
glittering with the magic of a thousand stars. Through the branches you
can see the clearing in which shrine of Elorna sits.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFENTRY
 IFITEM 1
 REMOVEITEM 1
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB STAND -1
 ECHO PLAYER You stand up and step back out into the clearing.
 MOVE 2531
 AFFECT 2531
 ECHO OTHERS %N rises from the bench and joins you before the shrine.
 AFFECT 2532
ENDIF
IFVERB PRAY -1
  ECHO PLAYER A sense of calm descends upon you as you close your eyes and meditate on the peacefulness of the great oak. Images of a hunters camp begin to form, empty at first but gradually, aelfen begin to appear, a pair of hunters bringing in a kill, some children gathered around a teacher, listening to a story about Elorna's warriors. A couple strolls by hand in hand,  their eyes smiling at each other. An elderly aelfen\
approaches you, a steaming bowl of stew in his hands. Bowing his head, he offers it to you, speaking "Welcome, kel of Elorna. Eat and fill your body with her nourishment. Rest, and fill your spirit with her peace."  Gradually, you begin to feel welcome among these gentle hunters, and when you finally open your eyes, you feel refreshed and strengthened. Amazingly, the steaming bowl of stew still rests before you...
  EQUAL ROUNDTIME 60
  NEWITEM 1 448 ADJ1=241 ADJ2=355
ENDIF
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
A fragrant smell drifts from the delicious looking stew inside the bowl.
Large pieces of tender meat are mixed in a spicy sauce with a variety of
pleasing vegetables.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB EAT 1
  CLEARVERB
   ADD FLAG2 1
     IFVAR FLAG2 = 1
       ECHO PLAYER The taste of wild game and onions fills your mouth as healing powers flows through your tired body.
       SPELL 318 50
     ENDIF
     IFVAR FLAG2 = 2
       ECHO PLAYER The taste of wild game and onions fills your mouth as healing powers flows through your tired body.
       ECHO PLAYER As you finish the remaining stew the bowl fades away.
       SPELL 318 50
       REMOVEITEM 1
     ENDIF
     IFVAR FLAG2 => 3
       ECHO PLAYER You have already eaten your fill, the tenets of the J'talth society preaches against gluttony.
     ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB RECALL -1
  IFVAR SKILL32 => 1
   IFVAR SKILL32 < 5
     ECHO PLAYER The Aelfen before you are J'talth, a tribe of warriors favored of ELorna
   ENDIF
  ENDIF
   IFVAR SKILL32 => 5
    IFVAR SKILL32 < 10
     ECHO PLAYER The Aelfen before you are J'talth, a tribe of warriors favored of ELorna
     ECHO PLAYER Kel are the warriors of the J'talth, dedicated to Elorna's service. They spend most of their lives in the field, defending camps such as this, populated with the kath, the teacher and healer caste of the J'talth.
    ENDIF
   ENDIF
    IFVAR SKILL32 => 10
       ECHO PLAYER The Aelfen before you are J'talth, a tribe of warriors favored of ELorna
       ECHO PLAYER Kel are the warriors of the J'talth, dedicated to Elorna's service. They spend most of their lives in the field, defending camps such as this, populated with the kath, the teacher and healer caste of the J'talth.
       ECHO PLAYER The J'talth are noted for their many herbal remedies, it is said that a day at the hands of a skilled kath healer is like a month of rest. Kath healing involves "hand, heart, and spirit", knowing that the body and the heart cannot be truly whole until the spirit has gained rest as well. It is this healing that has made the kel warriors of Elorna as strong as they are, their bodies rested, heart healed, and their spirit at peace for as long as they hold Elorna's teaching within...
     ENDIF
ENDIF
;
NUMBER 2533
NAME Inner Shrine
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
CHANNEL 115
*DESCRIPTION_START
Within the temple of the Lady of the Stars it is eternally
twilight. Slender marble pillars support a roof made of a
strangely translucent material that lets in the gentle
starlight which is the temple's only illumination. There
are never any shadows here, only the soft glow of the
stars. The only object in the shrine is a statue of Elorna,
crafted with an elegant simplicity that highlights her
beauty. Between each pillar you have an exquisite view of
the sacred grove, and a marble arch leads back out.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 60 ADJ1=187 VAL2=2531
IFVERB PRAY -1
   ECHO PLAYER As you murmur a prayer to the Lady a beam of sparkling starlight falls upon you, filling you with peace.
   ECHO OTHERS A beam of sparkling starlight plays over %N as %s prays.
ENDIF
IFVERB CONCENTRATE -1
  ECHO PLAYER Closing your eyes you concentrate upon the peaceful stillness of the inner shrine. The Lady's strength fills you and you feel ready to continue your struggle against the Darkness.
  ECHO OTHERS %N closes %h eyes in peaceful contemplation.
ENDIF
IFVERB LISTEN -1
  ECHO PLAYER You hold your breath and listen. The silence is broken only by the sound of a breeze in the trees and the occasional trilling of a bird.
  ECHO OTHERS %N draws in a breath and then holds it, listening to some inner voice that makes a serence smile appear on %h face.
ENDIF
;
INUMBER 474
NAME 77
MISC
WEIGHT 5
VOLUME 3
*DESCRIPTION_START EXAMINE
Made of purest crystal the tiny fountain glows with a dazzling rainbow
of colors emanating from its depths. The cascade of colors flows around
tiny streams of silvery water that fall magically from the top of the
fountain to its base. Highlighted by the magical waters and the beautiful
colors are two figures, a sensuous woman and a ruggedly handsome man.
The two beings slowly circle the base of the fountain, twirling slowly
in a dance of seductive intent.
*DESCRIPTION_END
VARIABLE montessia
IFPREVERB WAVE -1
  CLEARVERB
   ECHO ALL %N waves the tiny fountain about in a wide arc causing shimmering water to spray into the air where it slowly forms to combine into a dazzling rainbow that brightens the entire area with its shining beauty!
ENDIF
IFVERB CONCENTRATE -1
   ECHO PLAYER Your vision of reality fades to be replaced by a scene of a gentle glade where a beautiful woman and a handsome man lounge near a pool of shimmering water.
   ECHO PLAYER The man and woman rise to stand before you, their smiles dazzling.
   ECHO PLAYER The man says, "Greetings unto you, traveller from a far realm, we are the Spirits of Tessian."
   ECHO PLAYER The woman smiles and says, "Bound by magic and released only to dance when our master wills us to appear."
   ECHO PLAYER The man nods and says, "In the dance is the joy of life, let us celebrate it with you. In the hour of the rising sun, call us forth, and our dance we will share with you."
   ECHO PLAYER The image fades and you open your eyes.
   ECHO OTHERS %N closes %h eyes for a brief moment.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB RUB -1
  CLEARVERB
   IFVAR montessia = 1
     ECHO PLAYER The dancer has already been called.
   ENDIF
    IFVAR montessia ! 1
      IFVAR TIM = 6
        IFVAR GEN = 0
         ADD montessia 1
          ECHO ALL %N holds the tiny fountain aloft, you see bright lights spray forth from it to coalesce into the figure of a beautiful blond woman, draped in a diaphonous gown of white silk, who kneels before %N...
          PLREVENT 1
          CONTPLREVENT
          ECHO ALL Swaying slowly to some unheard rhythm the woman slowly rises to her feet, her hands sliding up the length of %N's body as she does...
          PLREVENT 2
          CONTPLREVENT
          ECHO ALL The woman gazes deeply into %N's eyes for a moment, letting her luscious lips form into a seductive smiles, before she gracefully pirouettes, raising her arms to the sky...
          PLREVENT 1
          CONTPLREVENT
          ECHO ALL The beautiful woman begins to slowly move, her feet stepping lightly in a graceful pattern across the floor, her gown billowing out to expose smooth flesh...
          PLREVENT 1
          CONTPLREVENT
          ECHO ALL The woman's feet begin to move faster, her entire body now flowing with the rhythm that has infused her soul...her hair whips out, descending slowly and catching the first rays of the sun, making them appear like gentle threads of golden wire...
          PLREVENT 1
          CONTPLREVENT
          ECHO ALL The woman dances closer to %N, sensously caressing %i with her own voluptous body as she begins to circle %i...
          PLREVENT 1
          CONTPLREVENT
          ECHO ALL The woman drapes her arms across %N's shoulders for the briefest of moments, her fingers dancing quickly across %N's chest and then retreating....
          PLREVENT 1
          CONTPLREVENT
          ECHO ALL Silvery motes of light cover %N, emanating from the graceful dancer who now slowly ascends into the sky and fades back into the essence of the tiny crystal fountain.
          SPELL 335 50
          EQUAL montessia 0
       ENDIF
       IFVAR GEN = 1
         ADD montessia 1
         ECHO ALL %N holds the tiny crystal fountain aloft, bright silvery lights flow forth from it, coalescing into a handsome, muscular man who kneels before %N...
         PLREVENT 1
         CONTPLREVENT
         ECHO ALL The man slowly rises, his muscles rippling softly across his body, his hands caressing the length of %N's body as he comes to his feet....
         PLREVENT 2
         CONTPLREVENT
         ECHO ALL The man leans forward, his lips tenderly meeting those of %N's for the briefest of moments before he leaps away, high up into the air where he tucks his arms in and rapidly twirls, keeping aloft for what seems an eternity...
         PLREVENT 2
         CONTPLREVENT
         ECHO ALL Landing gracefully on the balls of his feet the handsome man begins to sway in rhythm to unheard music, his hips slowly grinding and his feet moving slowly with a dancer's agile grace...
         PLREVENT 1
         CONTPLREVENT
         ECHO ALL The man dances across the floor, his feet, legs and arms moving together, in perfect counterpoint to his swaying body....
         PLREVENT 1
         CONTPLREVENT
         ECHO ALL The man dances towards %N, laying his hands lightly upon %h hips and slowly grinding the length of his muscular body against her...
         PLREVENT 1
         CONTPLREVENT
         ECHO ALL The man caresses %N with his body as he slowly circles %i, never letting his muscled frame leave her body...
         PLREVENT 1
         CONTPLREVENT
         ECHO ALL With a final caress of %N's neck, the man leaps gracefully into the air, turning into a cloud silvery motes of light that descend to cover %N for the briefest of moments before finally fading away.
         SPELL 335 50
         EQUAL montessia 0
       ENDIF
     ENDIF
   ENDIF
ENDIF
