INUMBER 531
NAME 316
ARMOR
WORN_ARMOR
WEIGHT 20
VOLUME 6
CONTAINER IN
INTERIOR 25
PARAMETER1 70
IFPREVERB LOOK -1
  CLEARVERB
   IFVAR INTNUM3 = 1
     ECHO PLAYER *** Be aware! This is a unique auction item!**
   ENDIF
    ECHO PLAYER Tiny beams of immense magical power hold the finely forged links of metal together, making the robe shift easily to the wearer's body. The metal itself seems to be some strange mix of randar, elkyri and some other unknown type.
ENDIF
IFVERB CONCENTRATE -1
  ECHO PLAYER A soft, hissing voice speaks in your mind...
  ECHO PLAYER "They once walked the caverns of this earth, glorying in the song of metal and the special talent they in working with it. The Dea'dhani, part fey some say, part aelfen others think, but the only thing known for sure is that their own beauty was reflected in the brilliance of their work. I was the last to visit their realms, before the darkness came...and was given this robe before I had to leave quickly...wear it well, wear it so their song will never die."
ENDIF
