 ECHO PLAYER You restore the trumpet's brilliant shine with a quick buffing.
 ECHO OTHERS %N restores %h trumpet's brilliant shine with a quick buffing.
 EQUAL ITEMBIT0 0
 CLEARVERB
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PLAY -1
 ECHO PLAYER A glorious peal of triumphant sound rings forth from the trumpet as you play it.
 ECHO OTHERS A glorious peal of triumphant sound rings forth from %N's trumpet as %s plays it.
 CLEARVERB
 IFVAR ITEMBIT0 = 1
  ROUTINE 2
  EQUAL ITEMBIT0 0
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PUSH -1
  CLEARVERB
   IFVAR INTNUM3 = 354
     ECHO PLAYER Scintillating notes of the purest clarity flow from the trumpet, rising into the air where they swirl like dancing motes of golden light before taking on the form of Yarin for a brief moment.
     ECHO OTHERS Scintillating notes of the purest clarity flow from %N's trumpet as %s plays it, rising into the air where they swirl like dancing motes of golden light before taking on the form of Yarin for a brief moment.
      ELSE
     ECHO PLAYER Nothing is accomplished by pushing the trumpet.
   ENDIF
ENDIF
;
NUMBER 1032
NAME Church
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
This room is unlike any church you have ever seen. Although there is an
altar, it lacks visible signs of statues or holy symbols that you would
commonly find in other churches. Rather the walls are adorned with
what appears to be the family lineages of different Drakin Clans. Heavy
smells of incense fill the room, which seems to have been designed more
for meditation than prayer. A gleaming statue, of a dragon rising above
a drakin male and female, rests in the center of the chamber. An unblinking
eye, set into the statue, keeps a wary watch upon the surroundings.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT NW 1028
ITEM 0 236
ITEM 1 346 ADJ1=423 ADJ2=187
EXTEND 1 of a dragon rising above a male and female drakin
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
The beautifully carved statue portrays a silver drakin with flecks of
gold running throughout its scales. Below the dragon are a drakin male
and female. The male is dressed in the style of an imposing warrior and
the woman is adorned in the accoutrements of a priestess. One of the
dragon's eyes seems to be almost alive, its unblinking gaze keeping
the entire chamber under view.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFVERB PRAY -1
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR RAC = 6
   ECHO PLAYER You sit down, close your eyes and open your being to the soothing peace of your ancestors.
   ECHO OTHERS %N sits down and closes %h eyes, chanting a soft mantra to %h ancestors.
   POSITION SIT
  ENDIF
ENDIF
CEVENT 64 40 1032
  ECHO ALL The watchful eye of the dragon passes over you, filling you with a blessed serenity.
;
